---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About Cameron Oliver | Fractional COO & Growth Consultant"
  description="Cameron Oliver is a fractional COO and business operations consultant who helps founders build systems that make growth predictable without burning out."
  canonicalPath="/about"
>
  <!-- HERO / INTRO -->
  <section class="bg-white px-6 py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-[1200px] flex-col items-center gap-12 md:flex-row md:gap-16">
      <div class="flex-1">
        <p class="mb-4 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-bright-blue">
          About me
        </p>
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold leading-tight text-navy sm:text-4xl md:text-[48px] md:leading-[1.1]">
          I'm an Operator, Not a Theorist
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-mid-gray">
          I've spent a decade inside fast-growing startups, from employee #3 to 100+, usually as the person leaders call when things start breaking.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex-shrink-0">
        <img
          src="/images/about-photo.jpeg"
          alt="Cameron Oliver"
          class="w-72 rounded-2xl shadow-lg md:w-96"
          loading="eager"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- STORY -->
  <section class="bg-light-gray px-6 py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px] space-y-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-dark-text">
      <p>
        My work has always sat at the intersection of operations, go-to-market, delivery, and product. Translating vision into the systems, roles, and rhythms that make a company work.
      </p>
      <p>
        After enough years in the trenches, the same pattern became impossible to ignore:
      </p>

      <ul class="space-y-4 pl-1">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="mt-1.5 h-2 w-2 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-bright-blue"></span>
          Founders making every decision themselves because nobody else had the context.
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="mt-1.5 h-2 w-2 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-bright-blue"></span>
          Teams working hard but not on the same thing.
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="mt-1.5 h-2 w-2 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-bright-blue"></span>
          Revenue unpredictable because nobody understood how the business actually created value.
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="mt-1.5 h-2 w-2 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-bright-blue"></span>
          Bad hires, unclear priorities, and founders carrying the anxiety of the entire company on their shoulders.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        Growth Map is my way of giving founders what I always wished every company I operated had:
      </p>

      <ul class="space-y-4 pl-1">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="mt-1.5 h-2 w-2 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-bright-blue"></span>
          A clear picture of how the business actually makes money
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="mt-1.5 h-2 w-2 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-bright-blue"></span>
          Clarity on what drives outcomes vs. what just keeps people busy
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="mt-1.5 h-2 w-2 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-bright-blue"></span>
          A practical way to make decisions week to week without guessing
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="mt-1.5 h-2 w-2 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-bright-blue"></span>
          A path to grow without chaos or burnout
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHY ME -->
  <section class="bg-white px-6 py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px]">
      <h2 class="text-center text-2xl font-bold text-navy md:text-3xl">Why Work With Me Instead Of...</h2>
      <div class="mt-10 space-y-8">
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-gray-100 p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-navy">"Why not hire a full-time COO?"</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 leading-relaxed text-dark-text">
            A good full-time COO costs $200K-$400K+ and takes months to ramp up. Most founders at $1M-$10M don't need a full-time executive. They need someone who's done this before, can build the system fast, and transfer ownership to their existing team.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-gray-100 p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-navy">"Why not just read a business book or take a course?"</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 leading-relaxed text-dark-text">
            Books give you frameworks. I give you implementation. The gap between knowing what to do and actually doing it inside a messy, real business is where I live. I've built operating systems inside fast-growing companies, not in a classroom.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-gray-100 p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-navy">"Why not use a big consulting firm?"</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 leading-relaxed text-dark-text">
            Big firms send you junior analysts who produce slide decks. I do the work myself, in the trenches with your team. You get a senior operator, not a presentation.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="bg-light-gray px-6 py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[600px] text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy md:text-3xl">If This Resonates, Let's Talk</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg leading-relaxed text-mid-gray">
        Book a free 30-minute call. We'll talk through where your business is and what might help.
      </p>
      <a
        href="https://calendar.notion.so/meet/cameronearloliver/qc3y04oud"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="mt-6 inline-block rounded-lg bg-bright-blue px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-white transition-colors hover:bg-[#0088c2]"
      >
        Book a Free Consult
      </a>
      <p class="mt-6 text-mid-gray">Not ready to talk yet?</p>
      <a
        href="/tools"
        class="mt-2 inline-block text-base font-semibold text-bright-blue transition-colors hover:text-navy"
      >
        Try one of our free tools instead →
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
